title: More English updates - Sept 18, 2014
message:
More English updates - Sept 18, 2014

NOTE!  I removed the duplicate CheckBoxPreference entries for Text-to-Speech (ttsspeed, ttsavgspeed, and ttsremote) in pref.xml.

New ones were inserted into a new <PreferenceCategory>, but the old ones were left outside of this <PreferenceCategory>.

I hope these are correct. The other language pref.xml files also need the update.

message:

* Removed "Manual monitoring: http://esya.ru/om/start/" (because I did not find a new URL to link to)
